    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in absolute pristine condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like paint finish completely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks, reflecting its life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the dashboard is flawless. Every single feature, from the navigation system to the heated seats, operates exactly as it did on day one. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a full, documented service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule at the original dealership. The engine bay is immaculate, and the vehicle sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example that offers a 'new car' experience for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
