      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total gem? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute beauty of a car, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014practically looks and feels brand new! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and is just waiting for someone to take it on its next adventure. You really have to see this one in person to appreciate how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out if you're interested\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
